{"word":"ἐπορούω","slug":"ἐπορούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπορούω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><i>to rush violently at</i> or <i>upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a><a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <i>to rush after</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>to seek</i> him, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; of sleep, <i>to overtake</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}